The Evergold is a magical fountain in Arborea shared by Hanali Celanil, Aphrodite, and Sune. It resembles a pool of gold-flecked water in a crystal basin, and wanders between the three goddess' realms. It bestows great beauty, but only for a year.
The Greeks call the fountain Canathas.
Sources
Dragon Magazine #60, "The Gods of the Elves"
Manual of the Planes, First Edition, page 94
Dragon #236, "The Seldarine Revisited"
Planes of Chaos, The Book of Chaos